{"tid":744694,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇倉鼠領養？","createTime":"2018-07-16T06:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T13:35:51.000Z","uid":31531,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9d7c2e650ce74d639b0477283a313f522410b58f","tid":744694,"uid":31531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:41:34.000Z","msg":"自己養緊一隻小露寶<br />\n所以都比較想知有冇小露寶可以領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他倉鼠都歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附上倉鼠圖三張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n湯圓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/143836_2e92f500f963296bc93e05db511709df.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F143836_2e92f500f963296bc93e05db511709df.png&h=0887423a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食緊提子乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/143944_14db1f5b51bb552102aea3c7f08238c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F143944_14db1f5b51bb552102aea3c7f08238c0.png&h=b292847a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想逃走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nb仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/144047_45b72c4b33cfd0c00fbb2bec636a9228.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F144047_45b72c4b33cfd0c00fbb2bec636a9228.png&h=4c65bfe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n琴日買返黎，今日走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依隻係好乖，可以上手既小露寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d472f40cbbf8b34a4d0deea35eadceedc56247d","tid":744694,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply